&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with workforce planning tools such as Anaplan, Adaptive Planning, or similar platforms&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Background in total rewards, compensation or HR analytics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience scaling people finance functions in high-growth, technology-driven organizations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proficiency in SQL and data visualization tools (e.g., Looker, Tableau)&lt;/p&gt;
