&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Education requirements: We require at least a Bachelor&#39;s degree in a related field or equivalent experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Location-based hybrid policy: This role is based in the San Francisco office with a hybrid work model requiring 3 days in the office per week. We offer relocation assistance to new employees.&lt;/li&gt;
